      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GIACOMO (1) dropped out early but hit the line hard, charging into third and beaten 5 lengths win (30.27) at this track in Grade 4/5. Has a strong record from this box. Goes very well from this draw with six wins and three minor placings from 10 starts. One of the contenders. AMRON DANCER (7) had been racing well with a Grade 5 H win three back then placed next time before missing the frame latest at this track. This looks easier and expected to improve sharply. PAW LOVISA (2) is worth forgiving for her last effort when sixth (30.17) at Wentworth Park over 520m. Solid record at the distance winning three races. Key runner who gets her chance to atone. SPRING MILES (8) is a last-start placegetter at big odds who will have admirers.",
